oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thomas Maupin and student buckdance at Summertown Bluegrass Reunion
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Thomas Maupin of Murfreesboro, TN, and an unidentified student buckdance at the Summertown Bluegrass Reunion, Lawrence Co., 2006.
This project was a TAC initiative and DeKalb was brought in to do photography in 2005 and 2006. Maupin is a 2011 Tennessee Folklife Heritage Award recipient.
